measurements.description: Sixty-two flat flowers and 42 buds on seven up to 26-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals white, marked dark red proximally, blushed dark pink distally, sepals broadly ovate, petals ovate-spatulate; lip saccate, cream, orange markings, side lobes red; column white, anther cap white; substance firm; texture slightly crystalline.
